   <text>
      <body>     <div xml:id="vicavNews">
            <head type="newsHeader">News</head>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">2.6.2021:</hi> With 20 new profiles there are now 106 profiles. </p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">27.1.2021:</hi> Entirely revamped VICAV 3.0 goes public. The bibliography has now 4722 entries!</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">19.12.2020:</hi> The Baghdad dictionary has now over 1100 entries.</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">1.12.2020:</hi> Shawi, yet another project building on VICAV starts.</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">5.4.2019:</hi> Bettina Leitner has contributed a new feature list for <ref target="feature:ling_features_ahwaz/Ahwaz">Ahwaz (Iran)</ref>.</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">1.4.2019:</hi> The <ref target="https://tunocent.acdh.oeaw.ac.at">TUNOCENT</ref>
               project starts. TUNOCENT (=Tunisiaâ€™s Linguistic terra incognita) investigates the
               Arabic varieties of northwestern and central Tunisia. It will run for
               four years and builds  on the VICAV infrastructure.
               </p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem"><p><hi rendition="#b">18.3.2019:</hi> Our bibliography has just gone beyond the 4000 entries mark. The 4028 bibliographic items contain 6304 geo-tags and 13.045 taxonomy labels.</p></div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p>
                  <hi rendition="#b">15.3.2019:</hi> New function to <rs ref="text:vicavExploreFeatures">compare features</rs>.</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p>
                  <hi rendition="#b">1.3.2019:</hi> The <rs ref="text:dictFrontPage_Baghdad">Baghdad dictionary</rs> goes online.</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">28.2.2019:</hi> VICAV has 41 new profiles, all in
                  all <rs ref="text:vicavExplanationProfiles func:insertProfileMarkers()">58 profiles </rs> now!</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">2.2.2019:</hi> The <rs ref="text:vicavExplanationBibliography">VICAV
                     Bibliography</rs> has undergone a substantial rebuild. All the bibliographical data is now also encoded in TEI
                  (P5), all the VICAV data now being available in TEI.
               </p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">3.12.2018:</hi> The cross <rs ref="func:createNewCrossDictQueryPanel()">dictionary search</rs> is finished.
                  It is now possible to query all dictionaries simultaneously.
               </p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">31.12.2016:</hi> The <ref target="https://tunico.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/">TUNICO</ref> project ends.</p>
            </div>

            <div type="newsItem">
               <p><hi rendition="#b">1.8.2013:</hi> The <ref target="https://www.oeaw.ac.at/acdh/projects/completed-projects/tunico">TUNICO</ref> project starts.</p>
            </div>

         </div>
      </body>
